***about de_carringtonvilla_pd***

Terrorists are on holiday at the carrington villa, But did'nt pay flight tax, Now they are wanted by several swat teams from different countrys....

Terrorsists are positioned all over the villa when they learn that the Counter Terrorsists are on there way to demand the terrorists pay the due flight tax, But the Terrorsists plan on blowing up parts of the villa that the dumb terrorists believe the counter terrorsists will use to gain access to the villa. These locations are. 

The main gate/entrance And the unmarked Helepad area.

HINT: if anyone needs more C4. Try the basement!

COUNTER TERRORISTS have actualy entered the base allready, and at two locations, So terrorsists stay clear of the windows, As one location is ontop of the mounting overview, Sniper heaven!   oh, and some other counter terrorists have allready arrived mysteriously at the helepad, however, no helecopter was ever visible. so the terrorists dont know...





****why I made it****
When I was younger, I played the Nintendo 64, And recently decided to stick an emulator and download some roms. Bordem works in strange ways.
well playing perfect dark, really inspired me to revive the third level Carrington Villa.
Anyone that enjoyed the game, or the level as much as i did, may enjoy being able to play it in css. Im concidering making it more detailed and having PvNPC single player for HL2 and just reviving the whole solo player game play. but maybe another time.

The Mafia is hiding weapons and incriminating documents in an old fortified farm, which was also used as a military bunker during WWII.
They're hiding the real purpose of the place with a wine shop business called "carpe diem". 
The police has sent a squad to take control of the place. The maffia should destroy all evidences 
and weapons before the police can grab them. 

*****************

This is my 1st CS:S map. I hope you’ll like it.
	
Parts of building in the map are originated from 'Shanhua Police Station'. 	
It is located at southern part of Taiwan, Shanhua District, 	 
which is a dazzling building causing my desire to create a map for it. 	
Nevertheless, due to its gigantic size, I can't place the whole building in to my map, but only the front.
 	
idea: 	
A truck containing highly dangerous cargo is lost it control, and then brakes in front of the Shanhua Police Station. 	
Mission: 	
CT – To stop TR from exploding the mass destruction weapon in the truck. 	
TR – Plan a C4 bomb in the truck to explode the mass destruction weapon. 	
P.S. The trigger of the weapon is damaged by the crashing of the truck. C4 bomb is the only way to activate the bomb!

To get across to the otherside you need to jump ontop of the train and jump off on the otherside, if you fall you will fall in the canyon and die.

Bombsite is under the train track, to get under the track T have to go in the tall building and go down in the hole. CT have to go in the bunker and go in the hole.

This is the second map I've worked on. The first was never released. (pretty much a learning/ testing map)  I wanted to do a relatively simple map and I've focused on game play more than details or beauty.  I tried to make the rush points interesting for shoot outs.  Both sides should reach the sandy bottem of Site-A area at about the same time withe the CTS just able to get into site(immediate site) /with shots possibly fired at them before entering or as entering.  Site B is indoors with a n entrance on both sides of the compound.  Cts can enter slightly faster than T's but shouldn't be fast enough to deny T's entry though the first T through may find a ct almost waiting for him (depending on spawn)  as for the middle route its a little more dicey with the ability to shoot and be shot at from compound and site-A area.  This middle route also offers the option of a window entry into site B  or a free fall with safe water landing   near site A.  T's also have the ability to rush and access the roof  of the Dam control compound and have a choice of 3  sunlight windows they can drop through.

Changes from version de_canyonbeta:

1: Limited walkable space
2: covered middle dam and changed natural rock formation bridge into a wooden covered bridge.
3: Added sand to impressions and flat areas  in the rocks above the valley floor.
4: Added extra route from middle dam to CT spawn/ A site. Now the ladder up to B isn't the only choice you have here. 
5: Raised the roof of the complex for more head space and tweaked rock formations for better/ longer cover and to tweak the timed meeting points or rush points making them slightly better.
6: Have played with Bots and seemed pretty sweet to me  

Hope you all enjoy- and if you Add this map to your servers rotation or voting system let me know I'd love to play it :)

Title                   : de_canal

Author                  : Flum
Email Address           : lars@johanssonart.com
Web Page		: www.johanssonart.com
Description             : A small and simple bomb map. 2-32 players
================================================================

* Play Information *

New Sounds              : no
New Graphics            : no
New Music               : no

* Construction *

Base                    : new level from scratch
Editor(s) used          : 3ds MAX 7, the GLB exporter and Hammer
Known Bugs              : Bad framerate in some areas and poor 
                          optimazation from my part, sorry :/
                          Pleas send me a mail if (when?) you find
                          any bugs :)
Build Time              : two weeks on and off
Compile machine         : p4, 3.0GHz, 1024mb ram
Compile Time            : 3:35 seconds

Summary of the level
====================
Tried to make a small but enyojable map that has sniperspots 
aswell as close quater fighting. The idea behind the map is 
that you should be able to play it with a small group of people 
and still have a fun time. The layout is keep simple but 
with a clear flow. it is planed so that the CT will have 
a second or so to setup the defence before the T arrive. a small 
but very importent advantage.
Enyoj! :)
